name: America's Most Eligible: Book 1
storyline: Battle it out in a reality TV show to determine who is most eligible! Create alliances, make enemies, even fall in love... the choice is up to you!
summary: America's Most Eligible: Season 10 is the first book of the America's Most Eligible series. It is alternatively known as America's Most Eligible, Book 1. It is followed by America's Most Eligible: All Stars and America's Most Eligible: Wedding Edition.
